nd verified. Here's the complete picture:"}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"**What's installed:**\n- **16 commands** available via `/geo <command>` in Claude Code\n- **5 parallel agents** that run simultaneously during full audits\n- **6 Python scripts** for citability scoring, PDF reports, brand scanning, etc.\n- **6 JSON-LD schema templates** (Organization, LocalBusiness, Article, SaaS, Product, WebSite)\n- **CRM webapp** (`scripts/webapp/`) for managing prospects through a sales pipeline"}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"**All commands ready to use:**\n```\n/geo audit <url>       Full GEO + SEO audit (runs 5 agents in parallel)\n/geo quick <url>       60-second snapshot\n/geo citability <url>  AI citation readiness score\n/geo crawlers <url>    robots.txt / AI crawler check\n/geo llmstxt <url>     Analyze or generate llms.txt\n/geo"}]},{"type":"heading","level":3,"children":[{"text":"🧑 You"}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"how do i access these skills in claude code. I dont see this list of skills in the customize section of the claude code settingd"}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"... and 24 more messages in this session."}]}]
